The holotype of 
<taxonomicName box="[461,713,1574,1596]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Decliviassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bipunctatus" status="sp. nov.">
