<emphasis bold="true" box="[720,800,1574,1595]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[720,800,1574,1595]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Style, lateral view; D. Subgenital plates, ventral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Apex of aedeagus, ventral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1701,2015]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Pygofer ventral appendage in lateral view with two posterodorsal lobes (
<figureCitation box="[1014,1095,1701,1726]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1572,1594]" captionTargetBox="[180,1400,201,1540]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[175,1411,193,1550]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 12. Decliviassus maculatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Apex of Aedeagus, ventral view; D. Style, lateral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Subgenital plates, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253721/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number box="[1067,1095,1702,1726]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
A), small triangular projection near mid-height, and more elongate ventral extension bearing apical notch (
<figureCitation box="[1025,1109,1738,1763]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1572,1594]" captionTargetBox="[180,1400,201,1540]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[175,1411,193,1550]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 12. Decliviassus maculatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Apex of Aedeagus, ventral view; D. Style, lateral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Subgenital plates, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253721/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number box="[1080,1109,1738,1762]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
E). Subgenital plate obovoid with slight concavity and small group of short fine setae at apex (
<figureCitation box="[882,964,1773,1798]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1572,1594]" captionTargetBox="[180,1400,201,1540]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[175,1411,193,1550]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 12. Decliviassus maculatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Apex of Aedeagus, ventral view; D. Style, lateral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Subgenital plates, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253721/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number box="[935,964,1774,1798]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
F). Style apophysis in lateral view slightly tapered to midlength, gradually broadened distad to footlike, obliquely truncate apex (
<figureCitation box="[1138,1222,1810,1835]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1572,1594]" captionTargetBox="[180,1400,201,1540]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[175,1411,193,1550]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 12. Decliviassus maculatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Apex of Aedeagus, ventral view; D. Style, lateral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Subgenital plates, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253721/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number box="[1193,1222,1810,1834]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
D). Aedeagus with shaft in lateral view slightly sinuate with low dorsal hump near base, margins gradually tapered toward apex; distal processes longer than maximum width of shaft, in posterior view extended laterad with apices slightly upturned, in lateral view extended posterad; apex in posterior view bifid, in lateral view curved slightly anterad; gonopore short, apical (
<figureCitation box="[233,314,1954,1979]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1572,1594]" captionTargetBox="[180,1400,201,1540]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[175,1411,193,1550]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 12. Decliviassus maculatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Apex of Aedeagus, ventral view; D. Style, lateral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Subgenital plates, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253721/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number box="[285,314,1954,1978]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
B, C).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
